column5: Steel headers weather.  Cold,wind,hail,snow,rain.  FINALLY  Now back to your normal weather watching channel Please do not disturb the short legged drifter  HAPPY HAPPY HAPPY

Oh come on, where is your spirit? Sitting here with the scent of fresh steel head smoking away. It,s almost like Christmas.
sitting beside him in a glass!
